{"tid":2178242,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「周庭bb入」黑警搜查日本《日經新聞》在中環的香港辦公室！","createTime":"2020-08-28T09:07:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T04:22:07.000Z","uid":222970,"like":200,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"9689e062b8b59a3ab0a5b45549ffec2a43d84669","tid":2178242,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:07:01.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"gold\"><strong>周庭 希望你睇到呢個post 麻煩你同日本嗰邊嘅議員講呢單嘢 仲有呼籲埋日本國民都要關注呢單野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</strong></span><br />\n搜《蘋果》同日　3 警據報持手令搜《日經新聞》港辦公室　涉去年眾志一則廣告<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/法新社-警搜查-蘋果-同日-3-警持手令搜-日經新聞-香港辦公室-涉去年眾志一則廣告/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%B3%95%E6%96%B0%E7%A4%BE-%E8%AD%A6%E6%90%9C%E6%9F%A5-%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C-%E5%90%8C%E6%97%A5-3-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8C%81%E6%89%8B%E4%BB%A4%E6%90%9C-%E6%97%A5%E7%B6%93%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%A4-%E6%B6%89%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E4%B8%80%E5%89%87%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A%2F&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyAUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=08607b31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%B3%95%E6%96%B0%E7%A4%BE-%E8%AD%A6%E6%90%9C%E6%9F%A5-%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C-%E5%90%8C%E6%97%A5-3-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8C%81%E6%89%8B%E4%BB%A4%E6%90%9C-%E6%97%A5%E7%B6%93%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%A4-%E6%B6%89%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E4%B8%80%E5%89%87%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A%2F&h=1bfd3d8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/法新社-警搜查-蘋果-同日-3-警持手令搜-日經新聞-香港辦公室-涉去年眾志一則廣告/</a><br />\n<br />\n警方早前以《港區國安法》的名義，動員 200 名警員，持手令搜查「壹傳媒大樓」，引來社會強烈迴響。<span class=\"gold\"><strong>據《法新社》報道，原來當日警方亦有持手令，搜查日本《日經新聞》在中環的香港辦公室，據報道，被搜查的原因是約一年前，《日經》曾接受一則以《香港眾志》名義刊登的廣告。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n《立場》正向警方及《日經》查詢，暫時未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n據《法新社》報道指，在 8 月 10 日，即警方搜查「壹傳媒大樓」當日，亦有 3 名警員持法庭手令，到《日經》辦公室搜查。報道引述消息，指警方搜查的原因，是因為約一年前，《日經》曾刊登一則呼籲國際支持反送中運動的廣告，該廣告是以眾籌形式集資刊登，而除《日經》外，該廣告亦在世界各地的報紙刊登。報道又指，該則廣告是以《香港眾志》的名義刊登。"},{"pid":"36cfcbbbfdf17751b2b6ec861bf3e639b4643a1f","tid":2178242,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b961d9d0f0d7e8687da09e4c4d9b4aee7b82db6b","tid":2178242,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:09:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc682148f23f291d1519943eab23bae17c66e78","tid":2178242,"uid":70786,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:10:10.000Z","msg":"追溯日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ec4114ba3b97378bf1c9fe55ce8ad1dddd11723","tid":2178242,"uid":144626,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:10:51.000Z","msg":"嘩嘩嘩, 今次又connect埋日本"},{"pid":"7af2fedf44e291a28ea9d6da928d1b551b7b7c8d","tid":2178242,"uid":222970,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:11:30.000Z","msg":"希望麻生太郎可以回應下呢件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa73e28d21b80ea50ace0a0062588e947046867","tid":2178242,"uid":214173,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:12:20.000Z","msg":"冇追朔期<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90dc63716e2132f2fbbc41705d1cef334b3895fe","tid":2178242,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20